---
// Démo Allo-Mission : maquette téléphone avec iframe — identique FR/EN
---
<div class="relative w-80 h-[664px] bg-slate-900 border-8 border-slate-800 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-6 bg-slate-800 w-32 mx-auto rounded-b-xl z-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 origin-top-left" style="width: 375px; height: 820px; transform: scale(0.811);">
    <iframe
      src="https://allo-mission.netlify.app/"
      class="w-full h-full bg-white"
      frameborder="0"
      loading="lazy"
      sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-forms"
    ></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
